Klasse ProcessingSet<T>

java.lang.Object
net.chaossquad.mclib.collections.ProcessingSet<T>
Typparameter:
T - value type
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Set<T>
public class ProcessingSet<T> extends Object implements Set<T>
A set that processes items that are added to it.
Useful for copying items for adding them to the set.
